## Key Components

### 1. Scroll-Reactive Header
- Fixed position with `z-40`
- Transparent when at top, glassmorphism when scrolled
- Back button: `w-10 h-10 rounded-full`, changes style on scroll
- Title: Centered, fades in when scrolled

### 2. Hero Wallet Card
- Pearlescent mesh gradient background (multiple blurred circles)
- Watermark icon (Crown) with `opacity-[0.03]`
- Large points display with "pts" suffix
- Progress bar with animated fill
- "Next Reward" info text

### 3. Tiered Rewards Grid
- Grouped by tier with headline showing tier name + min points
- 2-column grid layout
- **Locked cards**: Frosted glass overlay, centered lock icon in glass circle, gradient bottom overlay with text
- **Unlocked cards**: Clean gradient background, points pill, icon circle, title/subtitle, "Redeem" button

### 4. Floating Dynamic Island Dock
- Fixed at `bottom-6`
- Contains: thumbnail image, appointment info, action button
- Heavy glassmorphism
- Slides up on page load

### 5. Selection States
- Ring: `ring-2 ring-offset-2` with `--tw-ring-color: #D6A249`
- Checkmark: Gold circle with white check icon, scales in/out
- Button: Changes from white to gold when selected

